Timed out retrying after 10000ms: The command was expected to run against origin `https://qualityshepherd.com` but the application is at origin `https://app.featrix.com`.
This commonly happens when you have either not navigated to the expected origin or have navigated away unexpectedly.
Using `cy.origin()` to wrap the commands run on `https://app.featrix.com` will likely fix this issue.
`cy.origin('https://app.featrix.com', () => {` ` <commands targeting https://app.featrix.com go here>` `})`
